{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0028ef5276","title":"黄炎培斥子","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"20bc81cd6d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":30,"articleId":"0028ef5276"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"15c364a929","name":"清华大学巨浪社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ca791eb4df","type":"title","text":"黄炎培斥子","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"031852d1fc","type":"authors","text":"清华大学巨浪社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"f60c379c99","type":"paragraph","text":"本社记者，在电话中访问了黄炎培老先生，黄老首先表示了自己完全反对黄万里的反社会主义言论，支持全校同学对黄万里反党反社会主义言论的批判，并写信给中央统战部表明自己看法。现将黄老给中央统战部的信原文转载如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"f6266219ed","type":"appellation","text":"中央统战部：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"456b18c244","type":"paragraph","text":"承告清华大学同学们，愿约期来谈，谈的是我对于黄万里问题的看法，我是这样的：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"f0f8a4facd","type":"paragraph","text":"我在六月十八日看到那天北京日报载黄万里写“花丛小语”，当时就认为这篇文字太荒谬了，是反社会主义的，将会造成很坏的影响。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"6b188d396b","type":"paragraph","text":"我立刻严正地告诉黄万里，必须坚决站稳在无产阶级的立场上，深刻地公开检讨自己的严重错误，并将这严重错误快快地澈底纠正，不许再犯。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"062129a7a6","type":"paragraph","text":"我这几天连天开会，今天星期，上午下午都有会，分不出接谈时间为歉。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"16cf75d781","type":"paragraph","text":" 黄炎培1957．6．30上午","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"},{"id":"c10ae81a28","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《新清华》1957年7月9日。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276"}],"page":{"id":"ecff7f2c49","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0028ef5276","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}